    description: "Generate FDA submissions, clinical trial documentation, and regulatory reports more efficiently while ensuring accuracy and completeness."
  },
  {
    title: "Enhance Technical Communication",
    description: "Create clear technical documentation, API guides, and cross-team communications that improve collaboration between engineering, product, and business stakeholders."
  },
  {
